Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:25.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,りのん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:29.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:33.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,霧島君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:36.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここは私に任せて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:37.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to your elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:39.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩の言うことを聞きなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a knack for getting out of sticky situations.{I'm better at getting out of tight spots than you think.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:41.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こう見えても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:44.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,逃げ足には自信があるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:46.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:49.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.22,0:00:52.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The first alien I met...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:57.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,初めて出会った宇宙人は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:00.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とてもいい子だね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a really nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:02.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の親友なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna get in her way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:05.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの子の邪魔をするというなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:12.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すごいこと するわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.24,0:01:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:18.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:21.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
