Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:37.91,诸神-staff-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,日听：秋水无痕 翻译：yaya 校对：小草爱吃梨 Syura 时间轴：小青
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{part a}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go on... This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:39.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう 無理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:41.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,走れなっ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:42.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:46.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈美さん どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband randomly told me to come out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:50.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんか 旦那にいきなりここに来るように言われて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:52.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:55.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,車出してください ストーカーに追われてるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a stalker on my heels!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:56.96,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ストーカー？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make quick work of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:58.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなのこのあたしがちゃちゃっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:07.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ストーカー 大きすぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stalker's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,追手は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you check?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Still after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:13.92,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ついてきてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:14.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よしゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the others are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:16.62,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆 大丈夫かな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何 もう ついてる頃じゃねえの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They should almost be there by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:22.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん そうだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Ichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:25.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩 大丈夫ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:29.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we get over this mountain, we'll be at the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:33.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この山を超えれば すぐ駅に出るはずです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:34.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:37.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな また
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:38.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:43.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinna! No, wait.{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,りんな じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:52.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:53.96,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The anti-field is still active, so this is all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:56.34,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アンチフィールドがあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:58.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これぐらいしかできないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,行きなさい イチカ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,せめて 後悔をないように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:07.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.12,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あいつ まだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It can still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:12.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,りのん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,りのん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,行きましょう 海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:21.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,りのん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We can take this where we need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これで 目的地まで行けます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私のせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was so selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:49.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私のわがままのせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanigawa, Ishigaki, Kitahara...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.12,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,石垣君 北原さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemon, and Rinon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:00.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬 りのんも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:03.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆 ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:05.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,謝ったら ダメです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They all want to see your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:10.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆 先輩の願いを叶いたいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get there, we're gonna find evidence of alien contact,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:12.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆のためにも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.95,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その場所に行って 異星人の痕跡を見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you won't have to go back into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:19.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうすれば 先輩は宇宙に行かなくてすむ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We can all be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:21.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆一緒にいられる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫 うまくいきますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll all work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If things {\i1}do{\i0} work out,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もし 全部がうまく行ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I'll be able to go see your planet someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:40.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつか 先輩の星にも行けるようになるんですかね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,興味 あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そりゃありますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know where you grew up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩がどんなところで暮らしてたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and what your family is like. I want to meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.28,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,家族がどんな人なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,知りたいし 会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to introduce you to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私も 紹介したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What words would you use to introduce me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何って言って紹介してくれるんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:04:59.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,バカ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could've introduced you to my parents too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.72,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺も 先輩を両親に紹介したかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's fine. I have my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,両親のことは もう平気ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:08.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんもいるし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But sometimes I wish that I could've had more time with everyone together, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:14.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 思い出とか もっと作っておけばよかったって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,思うときもありますけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the reason why I want to use this to leave something permanent behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:19.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも だからこいつで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いっぱい いろんなもの残してるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how small it is. At least I won't have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちっちゃな 些細なことでも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,後で後悔しないように
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of memories in this thing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここに 海人君の思い出が詰まってるんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:34.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい 哲郎 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro, Tanigawa, Kitahara, Lemon, even my sister. Everyone's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,北原 檸檬先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:37.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆が入ってます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:40.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私も
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:40.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もちろんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ヒロインですから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I came to this planet, I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この星に来てね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当によかったと思ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆と出会えて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I got to meet all of you, hang out together, and make a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.97,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遊んだり 映画を撮ったり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういうのが楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish everything would stay this way forever and this summer would never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:01.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっとこのまま 夏が終わんなきゃいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:04.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんて 思ったりして
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell in love too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.29,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きな人もできちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, you became my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:14.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつの間にか 海人君が私の中心になってた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:17.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺も 真ん中にいます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't all fun and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.34,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,楽しいことばかりじゃなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There were hard times too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.63,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つらいことだってあった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,怒ったり 泣いたり
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I got angry, and I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be a lot more to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:28.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これから先も いろいろありますょ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We might end up fighting one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,喧嘩だってするかもしれないし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのときはどうする
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,仲直りします
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,絶対します
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're in love, you can overcome anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:41.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きな気持ちがあれば どんなことだって乗り越えられます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you always love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと 好きでいてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:47.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もちろんです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私も 海人君に恋してる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと好きでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:54.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,約束する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you say that one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今のを もう一度お願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:07.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は 海人君をずっと好きでいます
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,always love you, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:08.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...please love me forever too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと 好きていてね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:18.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:21.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誓います
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you'd be stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さすがに手強い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't think I'll just give u—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:35.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でもね まだ 諦めるわけには
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遅いわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:52.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,て 哲郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:53.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悪い 美桜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad news, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:55.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ガス欠だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫かい 哲郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.96,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その声 まさか聡さん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Satoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:08.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,聡さんって 真奈美さんの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that was Manami's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,助けて 聡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing's gonna get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:14.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,犯される
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:23.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but I'm not sticking around to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:27.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かんないけど このまま行こうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It really existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:51.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当に あった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.28,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:54.29,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place in my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の中にあるイメージの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:08:59.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっと来られた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっと見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:04.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:07.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start looking for proof, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:11.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,痕跡を探しましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:17.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:19.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that from the aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.69,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれが異星人の
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:24.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも これは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The way it reacted... That means... But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この反応 やっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:35.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,せ 先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.92,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これ 何なんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:46.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,見えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:47.96,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だって これは 私のイメージの中の
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the image in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,治療に使った私のセル
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used my cells to heal him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the proof we need!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,痕跡って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:26.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We came all this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:30.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,せっかく せっかく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks!{;_;}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the place Ichika and the others were heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:37.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれは イチカたちが向かってた場所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they break the spacial shielding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:40.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,空間のシールトが破られたの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:43.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だめよ イチカ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry and get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:47.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はやく そこから逃げなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:53.96,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't hurt him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:56.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やめて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:58.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その人を傷つけないで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:02.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう 逃げたりしないから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:03.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ダメです 先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:06.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やめて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:09.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう やめて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:10.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい 海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do this anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:13.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 もう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:16.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私のせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in danger! Everyone's in danger because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:22.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君を 皆を危険な目にあわせて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because I was so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:26.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,全部 私のわがままです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:26.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違いますよ 先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:30.32,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,言ったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆 少なくとも 俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least {\i1}I{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,don't think of it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなふうに思ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, I'm the selfish one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,むしろ これは俺のわがままです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,行かせたくない 先輩を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:51.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:52.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:59.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 この星に来たこと後悔しかけてた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,almost regretted coming to this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you all wound up in my selfish plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:04.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の勝手な思いが 皆を巻き込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the end, nothing came of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:08.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,結局 何も成し遂げられなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.63,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも やっと分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We all found each other because we wanted something to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:15.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私達 何かを始めたいと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:16.95,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お互いを見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちゃんと見つけることができた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to find each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always have these feelings within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の中に生まれたこの思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:27.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと続くわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll never go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:30.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,絶対に消えないって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,信じられる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:36.34,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:37.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:39.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺だって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you... too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichi—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:44.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:49.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,迎えに行きます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:51.28,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,絶対に行きます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん 待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:00.92,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:02.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:22.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,how long it's been.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どれほどのときが流れたのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But thank you for finding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.32,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:30.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,見つけてくれてありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:33.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これは イングローブから直接聞こえる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear it directly from the In-Grove...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I made an emergency landing on this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:37.48,盛夏-JP上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は宇宙船を乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The genetic memory of our ancestors has been released?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:37.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,受け継がれた先祖のデータが解放されて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}after I had trouble with my spaceship, and someone here saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.69,盛夏-JP上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この星に不時着して
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:42.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この星の人に助けてもらいました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, I had fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:46.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつしか その人は私の大切な人になって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a remote planet where contact with the locals is strictly forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:52.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも この星は原生住民との接触が許されない辺境惑星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Help will soon be on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まもなく 迎えがやってきます
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:14:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine my memories on this planet will be sealed to maintain secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密保持のため
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この星での記憶は封鎖されてしまうでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:02.48,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I wanted to leave some proof behind of the time we spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:07.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの人との思い出を残しておきたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の記憶が無くなっても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if my memories faded... Even if I couldn't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:12.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,思い出せなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to leave something behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,残しておきたかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for finding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,見つけてくれて ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray that at least my memories will live on in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:22.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の記憶が せめて あなたの思い出になりますよね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:26.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お願い 忘れないで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:28.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,忘れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,忘れられるわけない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:37.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと待ってるね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All we had
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:43.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それは ほんの数ヶ月の出来事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,were a few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一夏の出来事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All we had was a single summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:48.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの時の私達は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, we still hadn't done anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:50.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ 何もしてなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 何かしたいと思っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but we wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when Ichika showed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなとき イチカ先輩が現れて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and turned our summer into something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:03.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私達の夏を 特別にしてくれたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:06.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,喜びや悲しみ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy and sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:08.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すべてが詰まってる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...in that summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:09.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの夏を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:11.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺達は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.93,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(940,244)\blur0.55}Episode Twelve
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.93,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(647,77)\fs70\blur0.55}Waiting there, in the summer{\b1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...will never forget that summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの夏を 忘れない
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.35,signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs22\fnEdo\b1\c&H333927&\frz348.2\move(647,220,657,220,29,2448)}Castle Park
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.35,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\blur4\p1\c&H1D1D1D&\move(-6,18,4,18)}m 593 165 l 580 220 l 710 255 l 725 203
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Tetsuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:32.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎 これ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl in the class next door asked me to give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,隣のクラスの子に頼まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:38.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,受け取るなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What else could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,仕方ないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you give her an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:42.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちゃんと返事しなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, just get a damn girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,っていうか いい加減 彼女作れ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つってもさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio's good enough, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:50.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,美桜でいいでしょう 美桜で
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ウェルカムだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや まあ それは だな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny, Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:58.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,笑ってんじゃねえよ 海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.27,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ また明日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,気をつけてな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:07.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ 俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:09.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,またね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.12,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なあ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:14.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:17.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:28.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ 鍵 締め忘れたっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I forget to lock it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お帰りなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:31.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お姉さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただいま帰りました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How was Bolivia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうだった ボリビア
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a lot of work, but it was fun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.54,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大変だったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 楽しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:41.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい おみやげ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are some souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,趣味悪くない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I question your taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The doll is famous over there for being able to grant wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:52.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あら 願いが叶う人形って向こうじゃ有名なのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.92,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で これがイチカちゃんの分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:58.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういえば イチカちゃんは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,せ 先輩は その
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Her time abroad ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:05.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,留学期間が終わってさ 故郷に戻ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She went back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:07.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ええ そうなの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.54,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,残念だわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We could send it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ 送ってあげてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her address, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,住所は知ってるんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん そうする
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wishes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,願い事か
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,へえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're transferring away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,転校ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ええ 家の事情でね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Family stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't leave too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:49.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな 檸檬先輩までいなくっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So when are you transferring?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それで いつ転校するんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:56.63,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今から
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a farewell gift or anything, but this is for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,餞別というわけではないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:01.69,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたたちに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:02.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Film reels?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:08.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フィルム
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:10.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a truly wonderful summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:18.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当 素敵な夏だったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でもね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The movie is still incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,映画は未完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who has to put the finishing touches on the last scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ラストシーンを飾るのは あなたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:32.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悪いな 海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We came over all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,急に 押しかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:36.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいよ 今日 お姉さん遅いし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister will be home late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we all came here together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:41.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 久しぶりだね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆でここに集まるの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:45.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ 電気消すね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna turn off the lights, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:55.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:02.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,回すよ
