Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:47.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}I looked for the reason why I fell in love
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:54.63,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}and tried solemn words
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:20:01.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}Once I realized my feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:09.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}the threads had gotten hopelessly tangled up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:17.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}If I'd been able to say it without hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:23.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}you wouldn't have to cry now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:30.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}We paint a picture of feelings that pierce the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:39.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}Forever we will remember the scent of summer on the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:43.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}My memories of when I was with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:55.27,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}put color into my life, drop by drop, like the evening rain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People say that when someone dies, they go to Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:20:59.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,人が死んだら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:03.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}The things beyond my lens
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,天国に行けるという
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I don't think that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 僕はそうとは思わない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:11.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}seems like an otherworldly reflection
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When someone dies, I think that person journeys into people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:11.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,死んだ人間は きっと誰かの心へと旅立つのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:19.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}When I realized the feelings I'd lost
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They live on as a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:17.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,思い出となって 生き続けるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:26.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}our time began
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:23.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,けれど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}memories eventually fade with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:26.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それも やがては消えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why people want to leave something behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 人は何かを残したいと願うのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:34.27,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}No matter how I tried to balance our love on scales
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So others won't forget them. So we'll remember them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:34.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,忘れてしまわないように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:39.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}it never worked out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll keep filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:40.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕は カメラを回し続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:45.15,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}The sun scorches
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll record the continuation to what I already have
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:44.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フィルムに焼き付けたあの夏を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:47.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}the clouds with its rays
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of that summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:47.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その続きを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:56.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}and I wish for its warmth and brightness with every fiber of my being
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:59.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}I remember that summer like it was yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:02.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,393)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}and all my memories from my childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:16.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,432)\fs50\3c&H4A4948&}Let us take them both and let them fly far over the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.80,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(367,601)\blur0.6\fax0.15\fs25\fnTabitha\b1\c&H31332D&\frz15.693}Filming on Okinawa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{part c}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're playing the movie again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:52.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今年もやってんだこの映画
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the one the alumni left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:55.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,卒業生が残してたってやつ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:22:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:58.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺去年見たよ すごかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.38,0:23:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There were spaceships, robots, and a lot of special effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:22:59.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙船とか メカとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:00.92,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,特撮ばりばりで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the heroine's a hottie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:02.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あと ヒロインが美人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That all you care about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:04.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,結局はそこかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got nowhere to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:08.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,住む場所がない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:09.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そ そうなの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about you stay at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だったら 俺の家に行きませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I live on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:14.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 一人暮らしだし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have spare rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.07,0:23:16.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,家に部屋余ってますから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened to your spaceship?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.13,0:23:19.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で 宇宙船はどうしたんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:21.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,は？壊れた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?{aotyay^_^}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:23.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:34.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆さん 応援 ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:36.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
